definition: to rise/to raise/to get up/to set out/to start/to appear/to launch/to initiate (action)/to draft/to establish/to get (from a depot or counter)/verb suffix, to start/starting from (a time, place, price etc)/classifier for occurrences or unpredictable events: case, instance/classifier for groups: batch, group

sentences.english: There is a variety of reservoir types in the north slope of Chenjiazhuang Uplift.
sentences.chinese: 陳家莊凸起北坡發育了多種類型的儲集體。

sentences.english: The skull is well domed , showing a pronounced occipital protuberance.
sentences.chinese: 頭骨是半球形的，枕骨凸起十分明顯。

sentences.english: What causes the conversion and why does it have a convex casing?
sentences.chinese: 它爲什麼有個凸起的外殼呢？

sentences.english: Fig. 3.33. What is the unusual dilatation ( arrow ) above the right main-stem bronchus?
sentences.chinese: 這張片中右主支氣管上的異常凸起物是什麼？

sentences.english: A stone tool with a convex side.
sentences.chinese: 形石斧一邊凸起的石制工具。

sentences.english: Among them more outstanding of a characteristic be a desire association.
sentences.chinese: 其中較凸起的一個特徵是巴望交往。

sentences.english: We lose, he says, our 'youthful convexities'.
sentences.chinese: 他說，我們這樣就失去了“年輕的皮膚彈性凸起”。

sentences.english: The weathering resistance is strong, and the rock weathering surface often shows obvious uplift.
sentences.chinese: 抗風化能力強，在岩石風化面上常呈現出明顯的凸起。

sentences.english: To achieve the required bump heights, the solder paste is over-printed onto the wafer bond pads.
sentences.chinese: 爲了獲得要求的凸起高度，錫膏在晶片焊盤過焊。

sentences.english: Anticlines are arch-shaped folds in which rock layers are upwardly convex.
sentences.chinese: 典型地背斜是岩層向上凸起的褶曲。

sentences.english: His forehead domed out in a curve.
sentences.chinese: 他的前額呈半球形凸起。

sentences.english: He found a fast-drying paint to create raised borders.
sentences.chinese: 他找到快乾顏料去創造凸起的邊界。

sentences.english: Because stencils are impractical on bulgingbellies, he works freehand.
sentences.chinese: 因爲在凸起的肚子上用模板不現實，所以他用手畫。

sentences.english: A raised flowerbed can be built by laying wood in a square and filling it with compost.
sentences.chinese: 凸起的花壇可以通過鋪設在填方木和堆肥它建成。

sentences.english: During microdermabrasion, fine crystals usually remove the superficial or uppermost layer of the epidermis, known as the stratum corneum.
sentences.chinese: 能消除表皮上面的或者凸起的部位被稱爲角質層。

sentences.english: Microconvexes have been superposed on the daily variation curves of the water level in Suihua No. 2 well.
sentences.chinese: 綏化2號井水位日變曲線上疊加有微小的凸起形態。
